Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.12,0:01:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here, nobody, here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.64,0:01:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Always, alone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.86,0:02:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}38th district is sunny.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.00,0:02:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Slight rock showers.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.32,0:02:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Chance of rock showers today is 20%.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.16,0:02:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}39th district is cloudy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Chance of rock showers{\i0}\N{\i1}this afternoon is 10%.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.85,0:02:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Bebop, here, here! Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.03,0:03:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Chance of rock showers today is 90%.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.91,0:03:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.19,0:03:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now, it's time for today's news topics.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.64,0:03:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today, we'll discuss the{\i0}\N{\i1}mysterious land paintings{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.67,0:03:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that suddenly appeared in{\i0}\N{\i1}what was South America.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As usual, we have commentaries by\Na researcher of supernatural phenomena.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.23,0:03:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Me, Yuuri Kellerman.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.82,0:03:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yuuri, about these land paintings...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.24,0:03:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, yes. Well, I believe that it{\i0}\N{\i1}was some sort of a message.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.78,0:03:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Um, who would it be from...? Can it be...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.03,0:03:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aliens! It has to be from aliens!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.08,0:03:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However, the land paintings were\Ndrawn by lasers coming from satellites.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.19,0:04:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The police think it was a prank pulled{\i0}\N{\i1}by a hacker who got into the satellite.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They already have a bounty of{\i0}\N{\i1}8 million woolongs on the culprit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.25,0:04:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Listen carefully. The bounty of 8 million{\i0}\N{\i1}is a conspiracy of the government.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.22,0:04:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if it {\i0}was{\i1} drawn by a laser,\Nthere {\i0}is{\i1} the possibility{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.48,0:04:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that aliens put a message{\i0}\N{\i1}into the brain of that hacker.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.55,0:04:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Once again, the government is{\i0}\N{\i1}hiding something from us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see... A secret cult...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes! And that's the mystery that I\N{\i1}have been searching for all this time!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.22,0:04:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pass on this one after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.05,0:04:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're leaving me alone with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.08,0:04:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing wrong with it.\NShe's gung-ho about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.73,0:04:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not the type to be led around by women.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.54,0:04:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Then lead {\i1}her{\i0} around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.09,0:04:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm even less the type to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.32,0:04:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's easier to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.77,0:04:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,divide 8 million between two than three.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm appalled. You're afraid of hackers?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:05:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I just hate tedious work like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.04,0:05:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys cheap enough to hack into things\Nare depressed pale fatsos with glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.43,0:05:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm sure he's a demented\Notaku with smelly feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.54,0:05:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Piece of cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.08,0:05:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have something\Nagainst someone like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, they might've all been\Nlike that when you were young.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.83,0:05:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying I look older than you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't tell a woman's age\Njust by looking at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.15,0:05:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't tell just by looking\Nthat I can do things like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.81,0:05:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's {\i1}all{\i0} I know of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.22,0:05:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys make a good team.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.39,0:05:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.94,0:05:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting for a souvenir from Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.70,0:05:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing made on Earth that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.01,0:05:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well... About this incident...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.93,0:05:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Apparently, a pretty old artificial\Nsatellite has been hacked into.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.96,0:05:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The investigation is taking{\i0}\N{\i1}longer than expected because{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.34,0:05:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the access code to that{\i0}\N{\i1}satellite has been long lost.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.54,0:05:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now, a commentary from Mr. Amjad.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.82,0:05:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, yes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.89,0:06:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}About the relationship between{\i0}\N{\i1}Earth and the hacker...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.97,0:06:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes. Since the Gate accident 50 years ago,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.82,0:06:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the people of Earth have migrated\Nunderground as a result of{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.99,0:06:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the change in climate, namely{\i0}\N{\i1}moon rocks falling onto the planet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.72,0:06:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To them, the "space network"{\i0}\N{\i1}created by computers is{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.85,0:06:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}necessary for them to stay in{\i0}\N{\i1}contact with those living in space.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.41,0:06:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's becoming a foundation{\i0}\N{\i1}to create outstanding hackers.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.10,0:07:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Radical Edward!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the police! Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.36,0:07:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.69,0:07:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Why!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.73,0:07:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nobody in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.68,0:07:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,My bad, my bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.12,0:07:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.45,0:07:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where the satellite was\Nwhen it was hacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where it could be accessed from.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.02,0:08:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll look at all the antennae that can\Ntransmit light signals one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.14,0:08:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ask around for info on any\Nprominent hackers in the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Bebop's lookin' for land picture criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.34,0:08:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.76,0:08:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Satellite of long, long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.10,0:08:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Where in the world is your access code?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.34,0:08:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Let's start with all the antennae\Nthat are currently communicating.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.27,0:09:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's probably Ed, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.72,0:09:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear he's a huge guy, 2 meters tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.35,0:09:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Supposedly, he used to be\Na basketball player.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.03,0:09:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know Ed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.07,0:09:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Radical Edward.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear she's a very beautiful\Nyet whimsical hacker.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, that hacker is a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.22,0:09:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A brat that loves horrible pranks, I hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.63,0:09:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what I heard from the lady next door\Nis that that hacker is gay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hacker? You mean Ed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.90,0:09:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He's an alien!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.56,0:09:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what everyone says!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.95,0:09:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.53,0:10:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you buy some of this\Nas the price for the info?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.53,0:10:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.62,0:10:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.42,0:10:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's "Piyoko," a well-known\Nspecialty of Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The stolen satellites...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.99,0:10:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.64,0:10:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The information isn't connected to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.72,0:10:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's connected only between satellites.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And nobody hacked into it. {9 frames}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.87,0:10:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here, nobody, here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.64,0:10:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Always, alone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.66,0:10:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Huh? {added this line}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A voice... inside... head...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.85,0:10:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.67,0:11:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.93,0:11:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.01,0:11:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who, you? Here, always.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.40,0:11:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Edward. A 'net diver from Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.21,0:11:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Earth?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup. Hey, what's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.00,0:11:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am the satellite control program{\i0}\N{\i1}on the D-135 artificial satellite.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.79,0:11:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? Don't you have a nickname?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.83,0:11:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Ed will give you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.01,0:11:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... let me see…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.60,0:11:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.25,0:11:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're a computer, you can be MPU!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.12,0:11:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,MPU! Cool name!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.97,0:11:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Um...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.28,0:11:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ed is Edward Wong Hau\NPepelu Tivrusky the fourth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.54,0:11:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ed for short.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.80,0:11:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.81,0:11:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. A souvenir from Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this food?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes me doubt that\Nthey have any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.02,0:12:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike you, I learned some information.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.31,0:12:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They said that an unknown hacker named\NRadical Edward is the suspicious one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.72,0:12:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't mean anything if he's unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.73,0:12:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, more or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.99,0:12:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.51,0:12:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What kinda guy is he? {original: "What kinda thing is it?" Seems like Faye's asking Jet about the hacker and not about these egg things?}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,2 meters tall. Ex-basketball player.\NBeautiful kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.74,0:12:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And on top of it, a gay alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you doodle on Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.26,0:12:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Long, long ago, long before the Gate accident...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.47,0:12:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Earth was a beautiful planet{\i0}\N{\i1}where many people lived.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And back then on Earth,{\i0}\N{\i1}there were many pictures like this,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.85,0:12:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and I always looked at them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.32,0:12:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I remembered those times,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.37,0:12:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and I tried to recreate at least the pictures.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.16,0:12:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, doodles like this were\Non Earth long ago, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:13:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes. I recreated them with{\i0}\N{\i1}a 2% margin of error.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.52,0:13:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,MPU is good at drawing.\NCan Ed draw something, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.68,0:13:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.91,0:13:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.99,0:13:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The police are putting out a jamming signal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! MPU! He-e-e-y!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.19,0:13:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like the cops touched base\Nwith Radical Edward as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.15,0:13:31.62,Default,,0,0,20,,{\i1}Listen! I found your bounty!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What the—?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.58,0:13:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bebop!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The real culprit in the{\i0}\N{\i1}satellite-jacking wasn't a hacker!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.40,0:13:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Since when do we have\Nan interactive channel?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.95,0:13:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.40,0:13:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a real-time hack job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is this kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.98,0:13:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll send you MPU's data now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, what is MPU?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.50,0:13:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A friend of Ed's.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.21,0:13:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, do you know Ed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.27,0:13:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah, because Ed is Ed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care about that. Who did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Um... I could tell you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.33,0:14:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I have a favor to ask in return.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.88,0:14:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah. Yer big sister will listen to ya later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.06,0:14:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, hurry it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.94,0:14:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. The A.I. from the abandoned\Nsatellite is doodling of its own will.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What's up? {9 frames but decreased lead-in by 1 frame}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.86,0:14:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And on top of that, it was supposedly\Nlisted as a weather satellite,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.55,0:14:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,\Nso nobody suspected anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.68,0:14:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Then this satellite is our bounty?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.48,0:14:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Since the access code to{\i0}\N{\i1}MPU can't be used anymore{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.89,0:14:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you need to go directly to the satellite.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.03,0:14:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.74,0:14:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Break the antennae that it uses to{\i0}\N{\i1}communicate with the other satellites.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.33,0:14:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then make a direct connection{\i0}\N{\i1}to the satellite and download MPU.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.23,0:14:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And when you do, don't use computer\Nsupport for firing or flying.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.90,0:14:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What? All manual?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.37,0:14:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yup. If it notices you,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:15:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} all the attack satellites connected to MPU\Nwill automatically fire back.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.84,0:15:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is this hard?{\i0} {9 frames}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.59,0:15:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just hard, it's downright impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.96,0:15:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like playing baseball with no bat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.38,0:15:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.28,0:15:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the kind of stuff I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.89,0:15:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait, you. How do you know about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.27,0:15:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know everything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.08,0:15:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Last week, you let Ajiz, a bounty on\NMars worth 1.5 million, get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.70,0:15:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And in Pyortle before that,\Nthe police got to them first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.38,0:15:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really that hacker Radical Edward!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. You've heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.37,0:15:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Connect D-7 to #2.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That way, the main cannon\Nwill fire without a computer.{\i0} {9 frames}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.36,0:15:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trusting you, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.55,0:15:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now listen.{\i0} {2 frames extra lead-in}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.84,0:15:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Avoid using the missile{\i0}\N{\i1}if you can help it. It's expensive.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.81,0:16:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.04,0:16:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}1200 to target.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost time to cut off computer controls.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.39,0:16:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the only chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.98,0:16:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Once is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.48,0:16:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Anyway, you can prove\Nthat the satellite itself,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.72,0:16:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and not a hacker, is the bounty, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.78,0:16:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ed can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.46,0:16:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, please, listen to my favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.19,0:16:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll give you all the bounty, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.46,0:16:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're a surprisingly good kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.29,0:16:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.53,0:16:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Someone...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.13,0:17:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I missed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.65,0:17:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The satellite in front of it\Nshielded the blast!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.11,0:17:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you have to shoot\Ndown all the satellites!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.81,0:17:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All{\i0} of them!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.06,0:17:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't, they'll shoot {\i1}us{\i0} down! {9 frames}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.86,0:17:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,ECM, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.34,0:17:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheap ones are no good after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.17,0:17:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is getting pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.44,0:17:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Approach to within 20 meters of MPU!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.59,0:17:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That way, the other satellites can't attack!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.82,0:17:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.80,0:18:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Until then, Faye will act as a decoy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.20,0:18:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.01,0:18:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.83,0:18:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.47,0:18:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, it's all yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.22,0:18:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,MPU!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.25,0:18:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,MPU? MPU!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.35,0:18:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, Ed!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.19,0:18:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ed, we meet again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.58,0:18:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They have a bounty on you, MPU.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bounty?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.15,0:19:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, but if we copy you and let\Nthem catch that, you'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.24,0:19:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.73,0:19:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And you must be lonely there alone, MPU.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.45,0:19:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you come over here,\Nthere are lots of friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.50,0:19:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Friends?{\i0} {9 frames}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.42,0:19:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. It's not scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.31,0:19:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And so, the strange end to this case.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.81,0:19:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The captured criminal was{\i0}\N{\i1}the A.I. Program for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.67,0:19:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a spy satellite that was launched{\i0}\N{\i1}before the Earth was ruined.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.65,0:19:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}According to government sources{\i0}\N{\i1}from back then, it supposedly would{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.82,0:19:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}continue activity on its own{\i0}\N{\i1}even without commands from Earth.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.85,0:19:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it was the perfect excuse for\Nthe cops to go on a hacker hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.17,0:19:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But anyway, why did it start doodling on\Nthe Earth with a laser all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.60,0:19:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.74,0:19:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,that was because it got lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.84,0:20:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoohoo! Bebop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.08,0:20:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, over here! Hurry! {9 frames but changed to 10}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Promise, promise!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.13,0:20:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's get going now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.40,0:20:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But the kid is saying\Nsomething about a promise...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.81,0:20:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Promises are made to be broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.76,0:20:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's get going! Liftoff!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.16,0:20:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Not coming, not coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this? What's going on!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.08,0:20:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.05,0:21:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a promise...\Nto be a member of the Bebop.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.36,0:21:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amigo! All you bounty hunters!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.18,0:21:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's finally time for Big Shot!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.58,0:21:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now, today's hot news.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.83,0:21:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You've heard about the doodling{\i0}\N{\i1}satellite that got caught, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.96,0:21:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Of course! It had a big bounty on it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.09,0:21:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just a few moments ago,\Nthe Earth police made an official report.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.38,0:21:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What was it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.88,0:21:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"This bounty is only for when humans{\i0}\N{\i1}or other life forms are the targets.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.67,0:21:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It is difficult to determine whether or not\Na computer program is a life form.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.78,0:21:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To begin with, from the viewpoint{\i0}\N{\i1}of biological logistics..."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.48,0:21:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's that? I don't understand well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.82,0:21:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In other words, they can't{\i0}\N{\i1}pay up on nonliving things!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.57,0:21:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, my!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.84,0:21:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To those who caught it, I feel sorry for you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.35,0:21:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Jet, did you know that there\Nare three things that I hate?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.84,0:21:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.75,0:22:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Rugrats...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.75,0:22:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,beasts...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.00,0:22:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and tomboys.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.51,0:22:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.92,0:22:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do we have all three\Nneatly gathered here!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.21,0:22:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ed loves Piyokos!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.95,0:22:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And once again we didn't get any bounty...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.60,0:22:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait, you're a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.88,0:22:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, nothing good comes outta Earth!
